{"tid":702341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國料對中國加徵關稅 　川普將下重手","createTime":"2018-06-14T22:31:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T08:24:23.000Z","uid":147314,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e5224d19b5ec3ec4fdd0dae87a936dbb6e201caa","tid":702341,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T22:31:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201806150012-1.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F201806150012-1.aspx&d=4QFUcMGHpN3Zj9TGzmZjhv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=7cd3dbd3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201806150012-1.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>美國料對中國加徵關稅 官員：川普將下重手</strong><br />\n<br />\n發稿時間：2018/06/15 05:26　最新更新：2018/06/15 05:26<br />\n<br />\n（中央社華盛頓14日綜合外電報導）美國總統川普預定明天公布對中國輸美商品加徵關稅的清單，官員今天表示，川普料將指示對中國採取「相當重大行動」，可能影響價值約500億美元的中國產品。<br />\n<br />\n路透社報導，這位官員透露，由於美國如今已有直接與北韓溝通的管道，中國雖然對北韓頗具影響力，但川普不認為這是不對中國加徵關稅的有力理由。"},{"pid":"4b9850a075f20ebed14bce248ad1902ab6b5fea6","tid":702341,"uid":147314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T22:32:29.000Z","msg":"他又說，白宮下午就此問題舉行會議時，財政部長梅努欽（Steven Mnuchin）反對對中國加徵關稅。<br />\n<br />\n川普赴新加坡與北韓領導人金正恩舉行高峰會後，接受福斯新聞（Fox News）資深政治主播拜爾（Bret Baier）訪問時曾預告：「中國可能會對貿易議題有點心煩意亂，因為我們將在貿易方面下重手。」"},{"pid":"2510e87eaa4172df7509838a5f6e876a0877540e","tid":702341,"uid":147314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T22:32:50.000Z","msg":"川普預定明天公布鎖定中國500億美元輸美商品的修正版關稅清單。熟知修正內容人士透露，新版清單較最初版本略少，刪除部分商品，但也增添其他項目，尤其是科技業商品。<br />\n<br />\n另一名美國官員表示，文件草稿顯示，新版清單的課稅商品總額仍接近500億美元，約包含1300個產品類別，不過最終的總金額和產品數量仍可能變動。<br />\n<br />\n若川普決定對中國課稅，目前還不清楚會在何時開始啟動。數名產業界遊說人士對路透社表示，預料美國政府最快將在明天發布聯邦公報（Federal Register），公告對中國商品課稅，不過也可能延至下週。<br />\n<br />\n若華府對中國產品加徵關稅，預料北京會展開反擊。根據中國4月初公布的課稅清單，中方將對大豆、汽車、化學品和飛機等美國進口商品加徵關稅。（譯者：林治平）1070615"},{"pid":"d1e22ef122944913e3f6954390a5fc82419b2814","tid":702341,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T22:36:18.000Z","msg":"呢個中文版講哂，仲好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92a39104a47bb03d1d43078f34d2437693a75759","tid":702341,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T22:42:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbd0d6776573c3b5ccd535fea6f664bf7af5c656","tid":702341,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T22:58:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f64e6d41585a56de25e3b3244d8e2eed413be2d2","tid":702341,"uid":38049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T23:12:19.000Z","msg":"不過也可能延至下週<br />\n<br />\n係就快啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又等多一星期，你老味"},{"pid":"343027e2e80cd58789848e7bcd97d6aca17ef698","tid":702341,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T23:41:16.000Z","msg":"快架喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c8b5c94508e993fdc43bac05e8279458a67ece","tid":702341,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T23:45:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ccebed674fbcb0a65ea3b1849f21e4abb24c19","tid":702341,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T23:48:06.000Z","msg":"連你養嗰隻癲狗都收服埋<br />\n仲唔郁你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd2047802ad5fc80d2ad57bc0f691ec242e65189","tid":702341,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7ccebed674fbcb0a65ea3b1849f21e4abb24c19","tid":702341,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T23:48:06.000Z","msg":"連你養嗰隻癲狗都收服埋<br />\n仲唔郁你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T23:49:46.000Z","msg":"美國如今已有直接與北韓溝通的管道 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f994e7250a87002ed57bcee6e3e25de8432de6bd","tid":702341,"uid":37413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T23:53:38.000Z","msg":"又話傾好晒唔打貿易戰嘅<br />\n又話雙贏嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e9f174206e4051e55e56237d160c01e96094264","tid":702341,"uid":102179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T23:55:17.000Z","msg":"好難捉摸呀.jpg<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fd28dd248852a8545fcc2fd08a15128c26fb3d5","tid":702341,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T23:57:51.000Z","msg":"【最新消息】川普已正式批准 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a64130798ddf758986b6af3b5f1383fee797ca78","tid":702341,"uid":147314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T00:14:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://cn.wsj.com/articles/CT-BGH-20180615073944\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.wsj.com%2Farticles%2FCT-BGH-20180615073944&d=4QFUcMGHpN3Zj9TGzmZjhv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=fb76b15d\" target=\"_blank\">https://cn.wsj.com/articles/CT-BGH-20180615073944</a><br />\n<br />\n特朗普批准對約500億美元中國產品加徵關稅 <br />\n<br />\n知情人士透露，美國總統特朗普已批准對約500億美元中國產品加徵關稅，美國因而加大對中國的貿易攻勢。但目前尚不清楚加徵關稅措施何時生效。<br />\n<br />\nBob Davis / Peter Nicholas<br />\n<br />\n2018年6月15日07:45 CST 更新"},{"pid":"58b73cfc9bde5775f264e41ea2f4ae7af75bdc5a","tid":702341,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T00:16:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0fe781b42cc4eb28f2b6654ec9c524a00582460","tid":702341,"uid":147314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"58b73cfc9bde5775f264e41ea2f4ae7af75bdc5a","tid":702341,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T00:16:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T00:22:55.000Z","msg":"應該聽日正式公布 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d47dd0e2109efe295d50c05eeb7f494ef1cfd56","tid":702341,"uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T00:29:10.000Z","msg":"因應美開徵懲罰性高關稅 中國緊急決定擴大進口<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/business/breakingnews/2457596\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fbreakingnews%2F2457596&d=4QFUcMGHpN3Zj9TGzmZjhv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=8860df8f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fbreakingnews%2F2457596&h=2f0c6353\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/business/breakingnews/2457596</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國預定最快最明天（6月15日）起，對中國進口貨物徵收懲罰性高關稅，導致美中關係再陷緊張，為因應這一舉措，中國國務院昨天（6月13日）舉行會議，決定擴大一系列進口，會議還特別強調，重申維護自由貿易。<br />\n<br />\n綜合中媒報導，昨天的會議由國務院總理李克強主持，確定擴大進口的產品包括有關民生的日用消費品、醫藥和康復、養老護理等設備進口，也將落實降低部分商品進口稅率措施；同時確定，將大力發展新興服務貿易，促進研發設計、物流、諮詢服務、節能環保等生產性服務進口，並增加有助於轉型發展的技術裝備進口，並設法掃除進口環節中的不合理的管理及收費。<br />\n<br />\n另外，支持跨境電商、擴大免稅品進口、及強化知識產權保護等，都是會議中特地提到的項目。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不如直接宣布投降"},{"pid":"51832dcd4b972b2381e49a7de4022798b922e384","tid":702341,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d47dd0e2109efe295d50c05eeb7f494ef1cfd56","tid":702341,"uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T00:29:10.000Z","msg":"因應美開徵懲罰性高關稅 中國緊急決定擴大進口<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/business/breakingnews/2457596\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fbreakingnews%2F2457596&d=4QFUcMGHpN3Zj9TGzmZjhv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=8860df8f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fbreakingnews%2F2457596&h=2f0c6353\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/business/breakingnews/2457596</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國預定最快最明天（6月15日）起，對中國進口貨物徵收懲罰性高關稅，導致美中關係再陷緊張，為因應這一舉措，中國國務院昨天（6月13日）舉行會議，決定擴大一系列進口，會議還特別強調，重申維護自由貿易。<br />\n<br />\n綜合中媒報導，昨天的會議由國務院總理李克強主持，確定擴大進口的產品包括有關民生的日用消費品、醫藥和康復、養老護理等設備進口，也將落實降低部分商品進口稅率措施；同時確定，將大力發展新興服務貿易，促進研發設計、物流、諮詢服務、節能環保等生產性服務進口，並增加有助於轉型發展的技術裝備進口，並設法掃除進口環節中的不合理的管理及收費。<br />\n<br />\n另外，支持跨境電商、擴大免稅品進口、及強化知識產權保護等，都是會議中特地提到的項目。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不如直接宣布投降"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T00:31:26.000Z","msg":"批NXP係最後求饒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c417924b6fa2386a0524165e4c43afaf5cfc98e5","tid":702341,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T00:36:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e724f22d6191decbf5859de8d8d19127fdf4bd36","tid":702341,"uid":41458,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T00:55:52.000Z","msg":"包埋香港唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n費事畀班沉默大多數又乘機拎著數"},{"pid":"c9802039a522385d185530a666a72130a240ab80","tid":702341,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T01:56:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f50498d9fd8f24d364346c3964e26883b056321","tid":702341,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T02:26:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42c825d02bd9b387c08e0481c8d16191574e81fe","tid":702341,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T08:24:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}